        "text": "22. STEWART was reinterviewed at approximately 1315 hours, 11 May\n1952, and stated that TYLER was with him and had witnessed the incident.\nSTEWART denied emphatically any falsehood in the story and stated that\nthe whole thing was the absolute truth."
      },
      "translation": {
        "text": "22. STEWART는 1952년 5월 11일 약 13시 15분경 재심문되었고, TYLER가 자신과 함께 있었으며 사건을 목격했다고 진술했습니다. STEWART는 이야기의 어떤 허위도 단호히 부인했으며 모든 것이 절대적인 진실이라고 진술했습니다.",
